 government and pursue policy targets determined by the government.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2021) 4aKlimagerechtes Bauen. 4aMasdar City. 4aStadtentwicklung. 4aVereinigte Arabische Emirate.  aAbu Dhabi.  aEco-city.  aEcological modernization.  aMasdar City.  aSustainable urban development.  aUnited Arab Emirates.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021 Englishz978311075419308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021z9783110753974oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831107493280 cprintz978311074904540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311074929840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110749298423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110749298.jpg  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0  DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075419-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021